{"verses":[{"number":1,"translation_zh":"大难,"},{"number":2,"translation_zh":"大难是什么？"},{"number":3,"translation_zh":"你怎能知道大难是什么？"},{"number":4,"translation_zh":"在那日, 众人将似分散的飞蛾,"},{"number":5,"translation_zh":"山岳将似疏松的采绒。"},{"number":6,"translation_zh":"至於善功的份量较重者,"},{"number":7,"translation_zh":"将在满意的生活中;"},{"number":8,"translation_zh":"至於善功的份量较轻者,"},{"number":9,"translation_zh":"他的归宿是深坑。"},{"number":10,"translation_zh":"你怎能知道深坑里有什么？"},{"number":11,"translation_zh":"有烈火。"}]}